#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kbruch; is a small program to practice calculating with fractions and "
"percentages. Six different exercises are offered as well as a learning mode."
msgstr "&kbruch; ni A Gitoya Porogaramu Kuri Ibara Na: Imigabane . 4 . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Arithmetic</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to solve a given "
"fraction task. You have to enter the numerator and the denominator. This is "
"the main exercise."
msgstr ""
"- in iyi Kuri A Imigabane Igikorwa . Kuri Injiza Ikibara na Icyita . ni i . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Comparison</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to compare the "
"size of 2 given fractions, using the symbols <guibutton>&gt;</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>&lt;</guibutton> or <guibutton>=</guibutton>."
msgstr "- in iyi Kuri Kugereranya # i Ingano: Bya 2 Imigabane . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Conversion</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to convert a "
"given number into a fraction."
msgstr "- in iyi Kuri GUHINDURA A Umubare A Imigabane . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Mixed Numbers</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to convert a "
"mixed number into an improper fraction (ratio) and vice versa."
msgstr "- in iyi Kuri GUHINDURA A Umubare A Imigabane . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Factorization</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to factorize "
"a given number into its prime factors."
msgstr "- in iyi Kuri A Umubare Cya mbere: . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Percentage</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to calculate "
"percentages."
msgstr "- in iyi Kuri Kugereranya # i Ingano: Bya 2 Imigabane . "

